{"tid":500591,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"學人婚宴擺酒其實係咪要擺住心擺唔好計賺蝕","createTime":"2017-12-16T02:29:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T10:01:00.000Z","uid":71166,"like":260,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"ec6d5c9bf6311f280175239599967763a96f5fa5","tid":500591,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T02:29:35.000Z","msg":"我成日覺得<br />\n既然自己選擇擺酒就唔好care人地比幾多人情<br />\n你係請人地飲你倆嗰餐<br />\n唔係叫人請你倆擺酒<br />\n唔好乜人都邀請<br />\n你估個個都想去咩<br />\n要食酒席唔好自己去酒家食<br />\n講真我覺得結婚係自己家人嘅事<br />\n要請就唔收禮金 只請親人同最fd<br />\n係用個心請人食飯<br />\n邀請人地見證自己結婚咁先係路"},{"pid":"6f80c9147b6684f3bedd8fba9ce215f8ee233769","tid":500591,"uid":16061,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T02:32:08.000Z","msg":"啲撚樣就係想賺先擺"},{"pid":"05f2595573469df5f8a99a6bf5925d3b17eb2677","tid":500591,"uid":45290,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T02:48:21.000Z","msg":"一圍賺5000<br />\n舔舔脷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5870b9dec1ee84dc577640ba8e7b1f36dfb6730","tid":500591,"uid":45672,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T02:53:36.000Z","msg":"樓主思路正確。 所以我好多圍連大數都唔足12人<br />\n<br />\n預左蝕"},{"pid":"a5b6196527c9f8cc0297e2c76e8796eb394f027d","tid":500591,"uid":38302,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T02:55:19.000Z","msg":"５年都冇見－次<br />\n連你全名都末知叫你去飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb1c0ba3f3290ee52e1735b63abc85a90f9287a7","tid":500591,"uid":78429,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T02:55:53.000Z","msg":"上個月結完，只回到一半<br />\n擺酒賺錢呢一代真係好難做到<br />\n一係擺得cheap再博啲guest唔知<br />\n一係擺夠多人谷爆個場"},{"pid":"495c7f7055e567272095e9ba84e15ccbd315d8b1","tid":500591,"uid":130392,"like":3,"dislike":28,"score":-25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:04:44.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n我當年擺,人情只當係bonus<br />\n完全無預回本<br />\n擺得筆錢就預左俾架啦<br />\n我只請最親既親友+朋友<br />\n不過我擺每圍大約3萬<br />\n最後竟然嫌6位數<br />\n的確有d意外"},{"pid":"74c2d55950bd7d0565204af0f133c4deb1872bd2","tid":500591,"uid":130392,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:05:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同意<br />\n我當年擺,人情只當係bonus<br />\n完全無預回本<br />\n擺得筆錢就預左俾架啦<br />\n我只請最親既親友+朋友<br />\n不過我擺每圍大約3萬<br />\n最後竟然<span style=\"color: red;\">賺</span>6位數<br />\n的確有d意外</blockquote>"},{"pid":"43114d5e7fbd807643ec309242cae2ed9330ca04","tid":500591,"uid":45830,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:10:45.000Z","msg":"擺酒好多時只為滿足屋企老一輩所謂既慾望，你問下擺過酒果D，你估佢唔想煩少樣野咩"},{"pid":"d5129f6d3947456967f98317ed0df3bc72437e0e","tid":500591,"uid":126046,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:12:01.000Z","msg":"咪傻 冇可能賺"},{"pid":"23b8237184504e0f8c623e6299782387d1190a25","tid":500591,"uid":63883,"like":12,"dislike":4,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:13:59.000Z","msg":"個個都比人請去飲 唔通個個都想去咩"},{"pid":"aff64d0f26c7aeb356bc0993ac32713dbbee2ac9","tid":500591,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:35:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>擺酒好多時只為滿足屋企老一輩所謂既慾望，你問下擺過酒果D，你估佢唔想煩少樣野咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一開始多數係，但無可否認會多左難忘回憶，雖然好撚煩，但都有開心位。<br />\n擺酒預剩支出，人情當補貼就得，太著動賺蝕會好辛苦。"},{"pid":"31bf59de1f3d237d3a4a48fb2e0991009cc3e5ff","tid":500591,"uid":60136,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:37:02.000Z","msg":"打和"},{"pid":"8de37e77d2002e3d17eea6fa8365180ce3a6da25","tid":500591,"uid":97958,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:55:40.000Z","msg":"一直覺得擺酒係好浪費錢既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同一班唔熟既人睇一對唔熟既人做show咁"},{"pid":"340b5300b94db23cb0c696e9fd6f6f9bd4f44d32","tid":500591,"uid":22736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:56:04.000Z","msg":"有兩種一收晒晒禮金一種回晒禮金加主人家比多封禮是"},{"pid":"3e7dfd1bd9e196f188cea5bcad859f0987deb907","tid":500591,"uid":45672,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"