/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔洗出酒席仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc333acdd552c203ebc6353053300ea5106cf5a8","tid":500591,"uid":4761,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:46:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱啱喺富臨飲左餐<br />\n主人家擺成50圍<br />\n上網睇過頂多7千蚊一圍<br />\n當平均每人一千蚊人情都賺到笑<br />\n難為我地去飲既食埋d垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n擺明搵錢格"},{"pid":"267c6a53734db5407f87e5b4d99d0f14f01d0842","tid":500591,"uid":106675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:49:32.000Z","msg":"我鄉下習俗都唔收人請，人地嚟飲你個餐喺畀面你，係個guest送返份禮物賀你，鬼佬都係咁，整wish list 邊會送現金"},{"pid":"802e69964afbe14fbbf14e3f2c3b541d22bcc1d4","tid":500591,"uid":106675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:50:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱啱喺富臨飲左餐<br />\n主人家擺成50圍<br />\n上網睇過頂多7千蚊一圍<br />\n當平均每人一千蚊人情都賺到笑<br />\n難為我地去飲既食埋d垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雪雞 雪魚 又冇翅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b608738260a349fe384c3aa0e29dd8b65ba18f9","tid":500591,"uid":139965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:07:10.000Z","msg":"真心熟既 擺既唔會介意佢比得少<br />\n收帖既亦唔會比得鬆手<br />\n但通常收到唔熟既<br />\n果陣就通常去都唔想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ef016f82020839f86c268452229dec9d316c67","tid":500591,"uid":22024,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:20:54.000Z","msg":"唔介意比錢<br />\n但真係好介意要做場show <br />\n黎既好多未必真心祝福你<br />\n反而係係度評論擺酒既其他環節<br />\n野食好唔好<br />\n點解新婚套衫咁肉酸<br />\n去飲得多就知"},{"pid":"ca968980d30096ff52691e514170009fdcb30b7c","tid":500591,"uid":21035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:28:48.000Z","msg":"你<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請</span></span>飲，個心態邊有可能要人夾錢俾你咁... 人地俾人情係代表對你嘅祝福唔係分擔你開支，乜撚野酒樓800酒店1000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔通請人去你個仔嘅生日會又要分番M記100，Club House到會300咁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8499976d1d9abb27f3192d085f8438ae52987deb","tid":500591,"uid":56716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:31:46.000Z","msg":"有啲舊同學畢業咁多年次次搞聚會都唔應機，到結婚前半年嘅聚會又突然蒲頭談笑風生，結完擺完酒之後又繼續失蹤，我屌佢老母啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c719fb82ae3ec9220a2a1eecb461e05d2e4858f","tid":500591,"uid":8435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:35:13.000Z","msg":"同阿媽講過就算擺酒都淨係請親戚食返餐飯就算<br />\n寧願食好啲，唔會收禮金<br />\n佢即刻黑晒面咁話點解要唔收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身兩邊親戚都唔算多，加埋啲細路最多坐得四圍<br />\n同埋阿爸嗰邊啲親戚啲性格<br />\n就算唔俾禮金都知會俾返啲金器<br />\n最多咪5萬乜都搞掂，5萬都俾唔起仲結咩婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991860febbafc5202630126683f03c6d8824a9a7","tid":500591,"uid":72478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:54:19.000Z","msg":"結婚擺酒最無謂<br />\n同啲親戚朋友食飯咪算<br />\n最好就兩個人旅行結婚 簡簡單單最好"},{"pid":"4bffa1505bbda63f4633597efa0063b5575145b4","tid":500591,"uid":13257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T07:18:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>結婚擺酒最無謂<br />\n同啲親戚朋友食飯咪算<br />\n最好就兩個人旅行結婚 簡簡單單最好</blockquote><br />\n一向擺酒就係為兩家人"},{"pid":"f6f61b16832d674d05e91b20c0f179cff1738c74","tid":500591,"uid":97958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T08:08:49.000Z","msg":"最慘係明明唔中意做全場焦點，多人望下都覺得尷尬既人，點樣做全晚show<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得請自己中意嗰班人食下飯仲開心，俾唔俾人情都冇所謂"},{"pid":"895d2604236f821f7a1820052426785697dd68cc","tid":500591,"uid":117664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T08:31:30.000Z","msg":"想知其他國家係咪都要比人情<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee3e006a20a7029ad97e3b73bcc81da11b3fdb6d","tid":500591,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T08:33:49.000Z","msg":"肉酸到"}]}